                修补匠 工程师<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>|<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>|<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-3.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>|<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-4.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>|<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-5.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>|<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p17679664-6.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
